dimension: 29 x 20 in. (73.66 x 50.8 cm) (sheet, as printed)
text: This artwork is part of the series COVID-19: Labor Camp Report. Artist's statement on this artwork originally published on the @laborcamp Instagram account: There is always a new “executive order” around the corner. Another theft. Another self-serving scheme. Ulterior motives, half-truths, manipulative justifications. A trap.
title: August 11, 2020: NEW EXECUTIVE ORDERS
